{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"title":"removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","remoteS